individual« bis zu »public health« reicht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aEthnologie. 4aKultur. 4aKulturanthropologie. 4aMedizin. 4aPsychologie. 4aPsychologische Anthropologie. 4aRecovery. 4aSchizophrenie. 4aSinnstiftung. 4aSozialpsychologie. 4aTherapie. 7aPSYCHOLOGY / Social Psychology.2bisacsh  aCultural Anthropology.  aEthnology.  aMedicine.  aPsychology.  aSocial Psychology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2010-2013z9783110370713oZDB-23-TSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839416907zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839416907423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839416907/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013  aZDB-23-TSWc2010d2013